2. Planning Solver Forces All Passed Courses
The plan says planning should treat passed courses as decision variables, because extra passed courses may remain unused and only future courses should be penalized.

Current code forces all passed instances selected in planning:

optigrade/solver/ortools_core.py
solve_planning_cp_sat(...)
forced_selected_instance_ids=passed_instance_ids.union(locked_future_instance_ids)
This conflicts with Milestone 5.3 and can produce plans that are stricter or less accurate than intended.

